OL,3,CMeet the teenager challenging Adam
OL,4,CPeaty as both swim world-class times
OL,6,FJersey breaststroker Filip Nowacki has
OL,7,Fqualified for the European
OL,8,FChampionships, recording the third-
OL,9,Ffastest 100m time in the world this
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,FTriple Olympic champion Adam Peaty
OL,13,Fbeat him by four-tenths of a second
OL,14,Fduring the British Championships Final
OL,15,Fon Tuesday, but admitted that the
OL,16,Fteenager, who is 13 years his junior,
OL,17,Fhas a bright future.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/8
