PN,38602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1776359147
OL,3,CMeet the teenager challenging Adam
OL,4,CPeaty as both swim world-class times
OL,6,FSpeaking after the race, Peaty told
OL,7,FAquatics GB: "I tell you what, we've
OL,8,Fgot some talented youngsters coming
OL,9,Fthrough the sport, especially in this
OL,10,Fevent, so I know when I do retire one
OL,11,Fday, this event's safe."
OL,13,FNowacki, aged just 18, has already
OL,14,Fbeaten Peaty's British Junior Record
OL,15,Fand finished in 59.39 seconds at the
OL,16,FLondon Aquatics Centre to take another
OL,17,Fstep towards challenging the man who
OL,18,Fmany believe is the greatest
OL,19,Fbreaststroker of all time.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1776359147
OL,3,CMeet the teenager challenging Adam
OL,4,CPeaty as both swim world-class times
OL,6,FHe told ITV News: "I was just
OL,7,Fcompletely speechless with how fast I
OL,8,Fand everyone else swam.
OL,10,F"To go 59.3, a second quicker than I
OL,11,Fdid this time last year, was truly
OL,12,Fspecial and I was honestly stunned."
OL,14,FThe swimmer says he hopes to one day
OL,15,Fbeat Peaty in a major final, with
OL,16,Ffurther chances to impress at the
OL,17,FBritish Championships this week.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
