OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1776359147
OL,3,CMeet the teenager challenging Adam
OL,4,CPeaty as both swim world-class times
OL,6,FOn facing Peaty, Nowacki adds: "All of
OL,7,Fus youngsters are coming up, me, Max
OL,8,F(Morgan), Greg (Butler), Archie
OL,9,F(Goodburn), we do have a lot of
OL,10,Fmomentum and he's been on the stage
OL,11,Ffor a really long time, so I think
OL,12,Fwe're keeping him on his toes and it's
OL,13,Fgood to see that he's still got it.
OL,15,F"The standard is great and the field
OL,16,Fin breaststroke is so strong now, so
OL,17,Fit's really exciting to watch and be a
OL,18,Fpart of.
OL,20,F"I felt really good and to be able to
OL,21,Frace next to him is special."
OL,26,@pD@ApmpD@HpnpD@PpmpD@WpnqD@ApmqD@Jpn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/8
