PN,38605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1776359147
OL,3,CMeet the teenager challenging Adam
OL,4,CPeaty as both swim world-class times
OL,6,FNowacki will be busy this summer,
OL,7,Fcompeting at the Commonwealth Games in
OL,8,FGlasgow in late July before hopping
OL,9,Fover the Channel to Paris for the
OL,10,FEuropean Championships in mid-August.
OL,12,FAfter qualifying for the latter
OL,13,Fcompetition on Tuesday, he explains:
OL,14,F"I progressed a lot last year,
OL,15,Fespecially in the summer, so after
OL,16,Fthat it was definitely on the map for
OL,17,Fme and a target going into this new
OL,18,Fseason.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1776359147
OL,3,CMeet the teenager challenging Adam
OL,4,CPeaty as both swim world-class times
OL,6,F"I'm a bit relieved now I've made the
OL,7,Fteam, but obviously the job's not
OL,8,Ffinished."
OL,10,FDespite only being a teenager himself,
OL,11,FNowacki has recently become an AP Race
OL,12,Fambassador, a group co-founded by
OL,13,FPeaty to support the next generation
OL,14,Fof swimmers.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1776359147
OL,3,CMeet the teenager challenging Adam
OL,4,CPeaty as both swim world-class times
OL,6,FThe Jersey athlete says: "Once it gets
OL,7,Fgoing, I'll be doing a couple of swim
OL,8,Fclinics with youngsters in the pool,
OL,9,Fteaching them drills, how to start and
OL,10,Fpullout, just helping out and really
OL,11,Ftrying to move the sport on as best as
OL,12,FI can."
OL,14,FJersey swimming coach Nathan Jegou
OL,15,Fsays Nowacki is a great role model for
OL,16,Fthe younger ones to look up to, whilst
OL,17,Fthe athlete also develops himself.
OL,19,FNathan explains: "He's a bit of a
OL,20,Fsuperstar already and locally,
OL,21,Fswimmers aspire to be him.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
